Almost there, champ:
	1	The proxy only fixes CORS if you serve this HTML from that same Express app‚Äîopen it from file:// or another port and the browser blocks /proxy/*.
	2	You‚Äôre still sending OpenAI-style messages to Gemini and Claude, so those calls will error out.
	3	Host the SPA with Express and convert the Gemini/Claude payloads server-side, then the debate finally fires up. üü©











